      "comment": "ALLIE (7) has been hard to follow lately, running sixth (20.11) last time but prior to that ran very well when placed at Healesville. Meets a moderate line up and rates on top this time. NEVER SURRENDER (8) was always well back but did hit the line strongly late to finish 4th and beaten only 2.5 lengths (23.24) at this track. Comes through a solid form race last start. Has the ability to give this a shake. CHEER DOWN (4) broke a string of placings finishing in the money two on end before a last start sixth (24.69) at Traralgon. Form here at the trip sound including two wins. Will give the top chances plenty to think about. IN ONE MOMENT (6) will need to repeat last run to feature.",
